title: Meeting of the Minds: 2015 Quad MLG Conference (Marine Corps Base Camp Pendleton, CA)
text: ( Source : Marine Corps Base Camp Pendleton , CA) By | 1st Marine Logistics Group | October 13 , 2015 Brig . Gen David A. Ottignon, 1st MLG commanding general, began the conference by welcoming Brig. Gen Charles G. Chiarotti, 2nd MLG , Brig Gen .
